### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Criar Hospital
POST {{baseUrl}}/hospitals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Hospital Santa Maria",
  "cnpj": "12345678901234",
  "phone": "(11) 98765-4321",
  "email": "contato@santamaria.com.br",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 123",
  "city": "São Paulo",
  "state": "SP"
}

### 2. Listar Todos os Hospitais (paginado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals?page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc
Authorization: {{token}}

### 3. Buscar Hospital por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 4. Atualizar Hospital
PUT {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{token}}

{
  "name": "Hospital Santa Maria - Unidade Central",
  "cnpj": "12345678901234",
  "phone": "(11) 98765-4321",
  "email": "contato@santamaria.com.br",
  "address": "Rua das Flores, 123 - Sala 101",
  "city": "São Paulo",
  "state": "SP"
}

### 5. Excluir Hospital
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### 6. Buscar Hospital por Nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/search/name?name=Santa&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{token}}

### 7. Filtrar Hospitais (múltiplos critérios)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/filter?name=Santa&city=São Paulo&state=SP&page=0&size=10&sort=name,asc
Authorization: {{token}}

### 8. Filtrar por Cidade
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/filter?city=São Paulo&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{token}}

### 9. Filtrar por Estado
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals/filter?state=SP&page=0&size=10
Authorization: {{token}}

### 10. Listar com Ordenação por Data de Criação
GET {{baseUrl}}/hospitals?page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,desc
Authorization: {{token}}
